{"tid":1687443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃店經濟戰] 建議成立黃店聯盟","createTime":"2019-11-01T23:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T12:38:25.000Z","uid":143668,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a3774f4d828fdb320c3712aef4bfc42d99006cfa","tid":1687443,"uid":143668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:51:46.000Z","msg":"經濟戰打得如火如荼，小弟都想略盡綿力。<br />\n<br />\n參考形式:美國大學聯盟制度，如克萊蒙學院聯盟下的哈維穆德學院以及波莫納學院。其聯盟特色是<span style=\"color: red;\">資源共享</span>，倒如彈性選科，跨校/領域合作交流，共享師資場地等。<br />\n<br />\n商店好處:<br />\n1.降低成本。 實現來貨貨源共享，(向supplier壓價)<br />\n<br />\n2.集體宣傳:例如水門如清玉的互助/優惠成功帶動雙方名氣，這就是協同效應。提高店舖知名度都可以合理化黃絲子女孝敬藍絲父母食飯，多人傾黃店先引起到羊群心理<br />\n<br />\n3.資源再分配:分享貨源/用同一間物流公司可以令司機一次過運晒咁多間食店<br />\n<br />\n4.實現模式:地區聯盟/分類聯盟。地區聯盟比較簡單，即區內聯盟。分類聯盟即將不同食店/商店分門別類:例如日式/韓式/港式等。商店則可以以五金/士多等根據商店功能作分類<br />\n<br />\n缺點:知名度提高之後，或會成為藍絲攻擊對象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知大家點睇呢 抵制人血饅頭，人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75271626af595f4159a39ea8a125b485d344fd27","tid":1687443,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:01:20.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"76ec0485110279e060eaa87f1359fa047dcba0e2","tid":1687443,"uid":246279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:03:24.000Z","msg":"推咗先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pC3eKvG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpC3eKvG.png&h=4684a194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQcyZ33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQcyZ33.jpg&h=30ff9bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EJCQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EJCQK.jpg&h=41dfdbe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MeRTfCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMeRTfCq.jpg&h=f31aeaf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16717db0292f2ba6df320629b3ee4b051079a35e","tid":1687443,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:05:36.000Z","msg":"商會就係咁"},{"pid":"f711fd9aa0b88f0822510ffcfb51bc5da6db9dab","tid":1687443,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:14:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac269f971366b6d53eea03069b02db38f8b5836c","tid":1687443,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"77a43cba3a3797a971114f62875e101313e1b9b1","tid":1687443,"uid":234765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"推，希望快啲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523880af837a0c340ba3f805d600584e494071a5","tid":1687443,"uid":220260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c0aac554a388763f6427814ff5cc02a566d2336","tid":1687443,"uid":91603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:03:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd45cc38af4dcc780a41d7f7f86f5009d31f405d","tid":1687443,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7bc2f0f80a235d76db61ae5b4a48955654c3614","tid":1687443,"uid":146909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"[代post]飯堂老闆 之前有中一學生話得返三蚊上黎食飯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696407</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}